						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1546 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1468, Parābhava, Jyēshṭha śu. 15, Saturday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1546 A.D., May 15.</hi></p>						

						<p>It registers the grant of the <hi rend="italic">agrahāra</hi> village Minnikallu in Vinukoṇḍa-sīma of Koṇḍavīṭi-durga as a <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> to Annamayya, son of Tāḷḷapāka Tirumalayya by the king.</p>						

						</summary>
